<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I dont think people should sow for free if the recipiant can afford to pay.  If they are on a corpse run then i dont mind, but i hate it when people sow for free.  If you want to sow, play a shaman, druid, or ranger.  Otherwise pay.  Anyone who gives it away may help who their giving it to, but they hurt poeple also.  Every sow given away is money other people cant earn.  Besides why shouldnt i charge, if i didnt require a donation then i would have a crowd following me and i would always be oom.  Whats a little mana you say? whats a little plat.  I think that people who give it for free should be treated as scabs.<hr>Ragnorokk</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
