<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I am a 19 Shammie, and have always given away SOW.  It is not an unusal spell.  Druids and Shammies both have it, which makes it readly available.  I feel that charging for SOW would be the same as charging to swim in the ocean.  If a person feels they need to donate for one, that is there choice, I personaly will never ask for one.  I also Bind and buff for free.  Being like this has gotten me more in the long run I feel, then if I had charged for it.<hr>Woredin<br>
