<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Ragnorokk:<p>

Please keep charging for SoW! Why stop at 2pp? why not 20pp? You can charge 50pp for binds and 100pp for buffs! Just remember that Clarity will cost you 100pp, ports are 1kpp, and gods forbid you need a 39+ Res for 10kpp...<p>

Then, for fun, make a Warrior or a Paladin. You can now bask in the glow of paying 20pp per SoW just so you can run across Kithikor at night. You'll gladly pay that Cleric 10kpp for that Res you requested. You remember, he had that level 20 Warrior that you so graciously charged for SoW. Your warrior will shun those free buffs from those evil SCABS and look further to the honorable shaman that charges a mere 100pp! Please keep charging for SoW!<p>

Melee: Hey can I get a SoW?<br>
Me: 20pp for SoW, 100pp for SoW potion.<br>
Melee: Isn't that a bit high?<br>
Me: What do you think I am? A friggen SCAB???<br>
Melee: My bad, here's your 20pp. <br>
Me: Sheesh kids today! Only 20pp? I asked for a DONATION! You think 20pp qualifies??<p>

/rant off<p>

